description: Iris and Christie came to her house to inform her that her Tabunne might be in trouble as other Tabunne in the area had been disappearing. They put a tag on her Tabunne to track it in case it disappeared. Thanks to the help of Cilan and Officer Jenny (Isshu), when her Tabbune was being controlled by Team Rocket, they were able to stop Team Rocket and her Tabunne was returned.
name: Mao
